00:18:15.940 --> 00:18:16.539
Yes, sir.

00:18:30.460 --> 00:18:40.440
Why aren't you yelling at me?

00:18:41.340 --> 00:18:48.220
Well, nah. It's pretty clear you've realized you messed up.

00:18:48.680 --> 00:18:54.620
You got emotional, which is understandable, and forgot about everything else, which is also understandable.

00:18:59.519 --> 00:19:00.220
It's just...

00:19:00.460 --> 00:19:05.019
I felt too much, like I did in the sphere.

00:19:06.840 --> 00:19:08.660
I just had to take everything.

00:19:09.279 --> 00:19:13.000
No matter what people said or did, I had to hold my temper and endure it.

00:19:14.519 --> 00:19:17.799
But when they threw me away, I realized I couldn't do it anymore.

00:19:18.500 --> 00:19:20.500
If I kept holding it all in, I'd die.

00:19:21.819 --> 00:19:24.180
I thought that was enough, and I was past it.

00:19:25.620 --> 00:19:29.059
But I'm not. I'm still the same angry idiot.

00:19:30.460 --> 00:19:36.180
I thought that I'd learn to be better, but I still did what I always do and let the darkness well up in me.

00:19:36.740 --> 00:19:37.960
Until someone got hurt.

00:19:39.920 --> 00:19:42.559
So much crap has happened, but nothing's changed.

00:19:43.140 --> 00:19:45.360
Doesn't matter if I'm in the sphere or on the ground.

00:19:46.079 --> 00:19:48.840
Whenever I think I've grown, it's just me lying to myself.

00:19:49.920 --> 00:19:51.259
I'm just a piece of shit!

00:19:55.340 --> 00:19:56.759
I like hot chicks.

00:19:56.759 --> 00:19:59.799
Like really hot chicks.

00:20:00.460 --> 00:20:01.680
I'm not a hot chick.

00:20:01.680 --> 00:20:02.860
I'm a hot chick.

00:20:02.860 --> 00:20:03.620
I'm a hot chick.

00:20:03.620 --> 00:20:04.340
Smart ones.

00:20:04.960 --> 00:20:06.720
With all their curves in the right places.

00:20:07.100 --> 00:20:09.220
And with a stupid capacity for forgiving me.

00:20:10.120 --> 00:20:11.720
I love them so damn much.

00:20:12.380 --> 00:20:16.380
But when we start getting into the complicated needs of others, that's where I start struggling.

00:20:17.759 --> 00:20:21.559
And you know, no woman, hot or not, wants to hear that.

00:20:22.779 --> 00:20:26.079
Not being able to navigate that stuff is a personal failing of mine.

00:20:26.960 --> 00:20:30.440
So like all adults, I still have things I need to grow out of.

00:20:30.460 --> 00:20:37.259
The thing of it is, realizing when you've slipped up is kinda all you need to grow from it.

00:20:37.539 --> 00:20:38.440
Not that it's easy.

00:20:39.660 --> 00:20:43.559
I had to be brought face to face with my faults for me to finally see him.

00:20:44.039 --> 00:20:46.360
And you were cool enough to spot yours on your own.

00:20:47.220 --> 00:20:48.120
Know what that means?

00:20:49.740 --> 00:20:51.019
We're golden, baby!

00:20:51.519 --> 00:20:53.500
Cause we've got nowhere else to go but up.

00:20:57.500 --> 00:20:58.440
What do you say?

00:20:58.440 --> 00:21:00.259
When you're ready, we go apologize?

00:21:00.460 --> 00:21:05.460
I'm sorry about everything.

00:21:05.460 --> 00:21:09.460
We really did just come to talk, but we let things get out of hand.

00:21:09.460 --> 00:21:11.460
Are you feeling any better?

00:21:19.460 --> 00:21:21.460
You know, I love to chat.

00:21:21.460 --> 00:21:23.460
We could have one now if you still want to.

00:21:23.460 --> 00:21:27.460
I honestly love talking about romantic stuff.

00:21:31.460 --> 00:21:34.460
You talk how a good mama should sound like.

00:21:35.460 --> 00:21:36.460
You think so?

00:21:37.460 --> 00:21:39.460
Amo knows what a good mama sounds like.

00:21:40.460 --> 00:21:41.460
Amo had a good mama.

00:21:42.460 --> 00:21:44.460
Mama gave Amo her first love.

00:21:45.460 --> 00:21:48.460
He was who Amo got her treasure from.

00:21:49.460 --> 00:21:53.460
And why Amo saw the angel that goes between the sphere and the ground.

00:21:53.460 --> 00:21:55.460
Oh, that's nice.

00:21:57.460 --> 00:21:59.460
You saw someone go to the sphere?

00:22:01.460 --> 00:22:02.460
Wait.

00:22:03.460 --> 00:22:05.460
What did you just say?

00:22:30.460 --> 00:22:31.460
I did a thing Marie did.

00:22:31.460 --> 00:22:36.460
It's whenever you meet a girl you want to cut under your Jahreki.

00:22:36.460 --> 00:22:38.460
Yeah, I did that too.

00:22:38.460 --> 00:22:42.460
One of my fans already told me that he wanted to get her love.

00:22:42.460 --> 00:22:43.460
So how about this ..."I want her love."

00:22:46.460 --> 00:22:48.460
I don't believe he was just a tantalizer...

00:22:48.460 --> 00:22:50.460
about a nameless man.

00:22:50.460 --> 00:22:51.460
Asies precise.

00:22:51.460 --> 00:22:52.460
I was joking too.

00:22:52.460 --> 00:22:55.460
I bet she wasn't just writing...

00:22:55.460 --> 00:22:58.460
good-for-nothing emails.

00:22:58.460 --> 00:23:28.440
Thank you for watching!

00:23:28.460 --> 00:23:58.440
See you next time!

